      <title>特朗普贸易爆发，股指期货飙升，美元上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-06/equity-futures-surge-dollar-gain-as-trump-trade-erupts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着唐纳德·特朗普即将重返白宫，标普期货飙升，美元兑主要货币创下 2020 年以来的最大涨幅。瓦莱丽·泰特尔在彭博电视台报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-06/equity-futures-surge-dollar-gain-as-trump-trade-erupts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 08:49:27 GMT</pubDate>
