      <title>欧洲各国纷纷转向天然气，采取紧急能源措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/emergency-energy-measures-in-europe-as-nations-fall-back-on-gas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于风力发电量下降迫使各国重新转向化石燃料，欧洲各地的电价飙升。]]></description>
